messages.text: roach, u up?
yea, u wanna come ova?
I can’t sleep...started going over our last case
ur so weird
lol
how u been?
fine...how’s working with Brad
all right. hes good police
im sure
ur not messing with that shit again
im done with the white lady
good...ur good when ur off that shit
i miss us
so...u wanna come over?
i didn’t mean it like that...
dont be a tease, we were always straight with one another, weren’t we?
we’re not doin that anymore
ur the one texting me
we talked about this...
u talked
we cant be doing that
we’re not partners anymore so what does it matter
yea n how embarrassing was that?
people r already talkin that we banged and couldn’t handle our shit
who cares...
i like being a cop...this is my life...im not screwing that up
im not doing coke anymore...just come over
i need closure on this case b4 we let it go
hate to break it to ya, but its unsolvable
kinda like our relationship, rite?
let it go...
i cant...i got this feeling we’re missing something
even if you solve it - its just another drug dealer dead
cant hurt to go over it one last time?
come ova and we’ll go over it together
its over between us roach, professionally and personally, but we can end it on a good note?
fine. this is it though.
Ramone Casas. a small time cocaine distributor, sex trafficker, and scum-bag found shot...
in the back of the head execution style in the basement of his duplex house on 72 Laura St in South Prov
I love when u talk dirty to me...
get serious...ur a good cop when you try
No witnesses. The duplex’s other apartment was empty. Ramone used the duplex as a front to launder the money from his drug operation
what was time of death?
the coroner put the time at around midnight
Dispatch receives a mysterious tip at 12:30 AM from a burner phone that Ramone been murdered in his bsmt
they send a team over. House is empty except the bsmt entrance is bolted from the inside.
Theres no other access into the basement except thru that door
no one getting in or out. They bust down the door and they find Ramone and what’s left of his face splattered on the floor.
No murder weapon at the crime scene. No one else is in the basement.
First problem, how does the killer get out?
Or in?
The surveillance footage from the camera attached to the basement door, shows Ramone entering the basement at around 10PM and never coming out.
No one else enters.
Ready for mystery #3
Where are the drugs? The boys found fifty grand and all the usual baggies and scales, but no drugs
Why not take the money too? and again let me repeat...we have no witnesses who saw or heard anything
there has to be something we missed
I have a theory...
u have a theory?
now if we solve this, ur going come over right?
u solve this...ill wear those black panties u like
that’s dirty pool...ur getting me excited
what’s your theory, Sherlock? lol
i did it. Took the coke and murdered him
how’d you get out of the basement?
ill have that figure out by the time you come over in those black panties.
lol
what do we know about the bullets
the bullets were S&W .40 and shot from a Beretta Px4 Storm pistol...
which was not a gun found in Ramone’s immense gun collection
i did some research on the gun...before we joined the department the Px4 was the standard issued weapon
but the department switched to smith and Weston pistols due to a design flaw
u think a cop did this?
fits the evidence. this obviously was a pro job or someone who knew what they were doing and he probably was dealin with Ramone on the reg
pls tell me u haven’t told anyone this pet theory
just u, sweetie
so ramone lets the dirty cop in, presumably because he and Ramone were partners, except on this night the cop caps Ramone
takes the drugs, but not the money?
also, you’re forgetting that the security cam footage shows no one entering or leaving
I may have actually solved that problem
what have you found?!
if I tell you - you need to answer a question for me
just tell me and I’ll answer anything
pull up the security cam footage and look at the bottom right hand corner at 1:05, you’ll see a shadow just barely...barely but its there
I see it - so what?
go to 6:05 and u’ll see the same shadow flicker in and out, which means the video is on a loop.
The killer put the camera on a loop.
holy shit...you’re right
so...
do u still have feelings for me?
i don’t do feelings...u know that
that’s bullshit everyone "does feelings"...sum peeps just choose to ignore it
believe wut u will
u kno whats messed up is that u only had a problem with us once I got off the shit
that’s not true
all those times i was bombed out of my mind and u aint never stopped us, but the moment I quit the shit...when it got real
u filed to get a new partner said I was unstable
u beat a suspect near death because u thought he was flirting with me
that was the coke. im off that shit now
u want keep going or no?
yeah. it’s our last case
so how does our cop get out after he murders Ramone?
he doesn’t
wut?
if he’s a cop...he waits till the other cops show up and then he slips in saying he was on the scene.
great theory. but there was only one cop who was there before I got there besides the SWAT team
you.
id ask you if you want to come over, but im already here
holy shit - Ramone was ur dealer
i did it for u
how is that for us? That’s for u
we both kno the game. Every dealer gets caught sooner or later and I was going be Ramone’s get out of jail free card
u killed him
i did it for us
y take the coke?
coke is better than gold, babe, theres always going be a customer
ur going to go to jail
I only go to jail, if you tell
what makes you think that I won’t?
im willing to bet my life on it that you won’t
do you love me?
u kno I do
so open the door
r u high right now?
u want me to lie?
im sorry
shit
you have ten minutes at most
but you love me?
i don’t do feelings...I do the job.
it’s the only thing I can trust.
